'''David N. Magang'''  (o tshotswe ka 1938) [[Botswana|ke ]] agente/mmueledi, mogwebi le lepolotiki mo Botswana. O tsene dithuto tsa gagwe kwa University of London, Ke ene monggae/motswana tota wa ntlha go bula kompone e eikemetseng ka nosi ya molao mo Botswana. <ref>[http://www.phakalane.com/news/2009/aug/05/launch-of-the-magic-of-perserverance/ Biography:Launch of The Magic of Perserverance]. Phakalane ltd. website. Retrieved 2010-02-12.</ref> ke leloko la phathi e e busang: {1 }Botswana Democratic Party. Magang e ne e le Tona wa Palamente ya dikgaolo tsa botlhophi tsa Kweneng botlhaba /Lentsweletau go tloga ngwaga wa 1979 go eme ka wa 2002. O ntse le maemo a le mmalwa a berekela ka fa tlase ga bo Tautona Quett Masire le [[Festus Mogae|Festus Mogae]], go akaretsa Tona wa meepo le metsi (1994-97) le Tona wa ditiro, dipalamo le ditlhaeletsanyo (1992-94, 1998-2001). Magang o ne gape ele moeteledipele wa African Development Bank go tloga 1989 go ema ka 1992. Morago ga go tlogela puso Magang o atlegile thata mo go tsa tlhabololo manno/bonno , a aga the dikago tsa maemo a ntlha mo [[Gaborone|Gaborone]] kwa Phakalane.<ref>[http://allafrica.com/stories/200904150731.html Botswana: Magang Transforms Virgin Land Into a Paradise]. Mmegi/The Reporter (Gaborone), Lekopanye Mooketsi. 15 Moranang 2009.</ref> O kwadile buka ka ga ene kana ka botshelo jwa gagwe e e atlegileng thata e e bidiwang ''The Magic of Perseverance''  .<ref>[http://www.sundaystandard.info/search/search_item.php?NewsID=4216 A Review of David Magang’s “MAGIC OF PERSEVERANCE”]. Christian John Makgala, Sunday Standard. 18 Firikgong 2009.</ref><ref>[http://www.sarwatch.org/headline-news-for-botwana/177-mining-and-politics-in-botwana/1075-did-de-beers-cheat-botswana--the-masire-factor.html  Did De Beers cheat Botswana? – The Masire Factor]. Sunday Standard. 18 Firikgong 2010.</ref><ref>[http://allafrica.com/stories/200807140846.html Botswana: Magang's 'Unputdownable' Memoirs]. Mmegi/The Reporter (Gaborone). 11 Phukwi 2008</ref>

